headline: Sempra Named Among Newsweek's 'Most Responsible Companies'
summary: Sempra (NYSE: SRE) (BMV: SRE) today announced it has been recognized by Newsweek as one of "America's Most Responsible Companies" for 2025, earning this distinction for the sixth consecutive year.

headline: New tactic to close Aliso Canyon gas storage facility: Switch more neighbors to electric appliances
summary: State lawmakers implored community members to hasten Aliso Canyon's closure by consuming less gas and turning to electric appliances.
